race.comment: LOOKING PRISTINE (2) was below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.76) in a Grade 5, finishing a 18 length eighth. Has already won three times from this draw. Expected to be in the finish. LOTTIE ELLIE (7) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at The Gardens over 515m behind Fascinate John (30.48) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. Leading chance. MARSHALL KADE (6) filled a minor placing last start at The Gardens behind Fascinate Jess (23.56) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. VALKYRIE HEAT (8) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around.
